Attribution and Inspiration
---------------------------

This project is inspired by practical terminal-first developer tools, including
tw93/mole's approachable command-line ergonomics, and by public defensive
security practices around signatures, ransomware canaries, OS posture checks,
local-first tooling, and transparent release verification.

